"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇家人支持<br />\n更只可自己默默承受........."},{"pid":"4af7cf74261ef7743b0296e434b6f8bdfbf8cf8e","tid":415061,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:46:53.000Z","msg":"梅媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab3a30c7e58479769650acbf345c320852cc047","tid":415061,"uid":148360,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"吾覺 盡量令自己開心就得"},{"pid":"979bbe6030b70019c4842d9df5f61528f68bc608","tid":415061,"uid":69756,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔太後生了<br />\n唔會有依d感慨"},{"pid":"e1c245a79ea832733d65dba81cccc1e5871d0f8b","tid":415061,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔太後生了<br />\n唔會有依d感慨</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得知咁少人回"},{"pid":"14072526ee2e85e1eb7e0a061206aa3d8cda086a","tid":415061,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好鍾意梅姐 好想睇佢演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6302c575c2fe44efcd5177bc241adb12b319c2c6","tid":415061,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好鍾意梅姐 好想睇佢演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終有一日會再聚"},{"pid":"4057e0f357a32eacb53cb0aab239a783b40a1a7e","tid":415061,"uid":54038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"我認識剛剛死既飛機師 <br />\n睇左你個post 個心沉重左一下<br />\n25歲就咁離開左..."},{"pid":"111561d30258e730df5d6a26653345341f982a02","tid":415061,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"永遠懷念佢同哥哥<br />\n佢地去咗嘅嗰年 香港冇咗兩粒巨星"},{"pid":"4b19de5a3